---
title: Zesty Garlic Turkey  Sandwiches with Basil Pesto Mayo and Salad
description: Sandwiches are the ultimate hearty, hand-held food! Succulent turkey breast is seasoned with Zesty Garlic Blend,  then nestled in toasty sandwich buns. Adding juicy tomatoes and basil pesto mayo will make your sandwich dreams come true!
